<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
  <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">About Us</h1>

  <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Story</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
      Welcome to Acer Coffee! We're a small-batch coffee roasting business dedicated to bringing you the
      freshest, highest-quality coffee beans delivered right to your door.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
      Our journey began with a simple passion for great coffee. We believe that everyone deserves to
      experience the rich flavors and aromas of freshly roasted beans, and we're committed to making
      that possible through our subscription service.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Process</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
      We roast 1,000-2,000 pounds of coffee per month, carefully selecting beans from the world's
      best coffee-growing regions. Each batch is roasted to perfection, ensuring optimal flavor
      and freshness.
    </p>
    <p class="text-gray-700">
      We roast to order, which means your coffee is never sitting on a shelf. From roaster to your
      door in days, not weeks or months.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Commitment</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700">
      Quality, freshness, and customer satisfaction are at the heart of everything we do. We're here
      to make your coffee experience exceptional, one cup at a time.
    </p>
  </div>

  <% if @featured_testimonials.any? %>
    <div class="mt-8 bg-stone-950 text-stone-50 p-8 rounded-lg shadow">
      <div class="flex items-end justify-between gap-4 mb-6">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">What Customers Say</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-300 mt-2">A few of the notes customers have shared about Acer Coffee and the experience around it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        <% @featured_testimonials.each do |review| %>
          <article class="rounded-lg border border-stone-800 bg-stone-900/70 p-6">
            <div class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-stone-400">Rated <%= review.rating %> / 5</div>
            <h3 class="mt-3 text-xl font-semibold"><%= review.headline.presence || "Acer Coffee customer" %></h3>
            <p class="mt-4 text-stone-200 leading-relaxed"><%= truncate(review.body, length: 220) %></p>
            <div class="mt-5 text-sm text-stone-400">
              <span><%= review.customer_name %></span>
              <% if review.location.present? %>
                <span> • <%= review.location %></span>
              <% end %>
              <% if review.product.present? %>
                <div class="mt-2 text-stone-500">Originally shared about <%= review.product.name %></div>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </article>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</div>
